#. Tag: title
#: taskstatusview.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Task Status View is used to inspect task progress information at a "
"period, set in the configuration."
msgstr ""
"Pogled stanja naloge se uporablja za pregled informacij o napredku naloge v "
"obdobju, ki je nastavljeno v konfiguraciji."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tasks are divided into groups dependent on the status of the task:"
msgstr "Naloge so razdeljene v skupine glede na stanje naloge:"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not Started"
msgstr "Ni se začelo"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that should have been started by now."
msgstr "Naloge, ki bi jih zdaj že morali začeti."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running"
msgstr "V teku"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that have been started, but not yet finished."
msgstr "Naloge, ki so bile začete, a še niso dokončane."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Dokončano"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that were finished in this period"
msgstr "Naloge, ki so bile v tem obdobju končane"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next Period"
msgstr "Naslednje obdobje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that are scheduled to be started in the next period."
msgstr "Naloge, ki so načrtovane za začetek v naslednjem obdobju."

#. Tag: title
#: taskstatusview.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Progress information can be edited in-line as described <link linkend="
"\"using-the-views\">here</link> or by using the task progress dialog."
msgstr ""
"Podatke o napredku je mogoče urejati neposredno, kot je opisano <link "
"linkend=\"using-the-views\">tukaj</link>, ali v pogovornem oknu napredka "
"naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Naslednji stolpci so privzeto prikazani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskstatusview.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Stolpec"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: taskstatusview.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the task."
msgstr "Ime naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task status"
msgstr "Stanje naloge"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "% Completion"
msgstr "% dokončanja"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task completion"
msgstr "Dokončanje naloge"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Effort"
msgstr "Načrtovani napor"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of work planned to be used at the end of the current period."
msgstr "Količina dela, načrtovana za uporabo ob koncu tekočega obdobja."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Effort"
msgstr "Dejanski napor"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of work spent."
msgstr "Količina porabljenega dela."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remaining Effort"
msgstr "Preostali napor"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The remaining effort needed to complete the task."
msgstr "Preostali napor, potreben za dokončanje naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Cost"
msgstr "Načrtovani stroški"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "The planned cost at the end of the current period."
msgstr "Načrtovani stroški ob koncu tekočega obdobja."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Cost"
msgstr "Dejanski stroški"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual cost incurred."
msgstr "Dejanski nastali stroški."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Start"
msgstr "Dejanski začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual start time of the task."
msgstr "Dejanski začetni čas naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Finish"
msgstr "Dejanski zaključek"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual finish time of the task."
msgstr "Dejanski končni čas naloge."

#. Tag: title
#: taskstatusview.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to split / unsplit the "
"tree view or it can be configured using the configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"S kontekstnim menijem lahko pogled konfigurirate tako, da razdeli/razdeli "
"drevesni pogled, ali pa ga konfigurirate v pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: taskstatusview.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da količino informacij, ki jih "
"prikaže pogled, prilagodite svojim potrebam."
